        •	Every month Purav Bhadra Nakshatram – Anjaneya Swamy Thirumanjanam. <br />
        •	Every Pournima – Lakshmi Hayagriva Thirumanjanam. <br />
        •	Every Friday – Sarva Mangala Devi Thirumanjanam. <br />
        •	Every Tuesday & Saturday – Sindhuraachana for Anjaneya (Chandanarchana). <br />
