        •	Every Saturday – Vasudeva, Sudarshana, Narasimha Havanam & Palaki Seva for Srinivas Perumal. <br />
        •	Every Tuesday – Sri Rama Hanumat Moola Mantra Havanam. <br />
        •	Every Friday – Maha Lakshmi Kumkuma Archana. <br />


        •	SV Temple SRD was established to propagate the Hindu dharma and also helps promote the age-old cultural heritage of India, <br />
